prompts.create_request:
Create a complete API request example:

API: {api_name}
Endpoint: {endpoint}
Method: {method}
Authentication: {auth_type}
Purpose: {purpose}

Generate:
1. Full URL with query parameters
2. Headers (including auth)
3. Request body (if POST/PUT/PATCH)
4. Example using curl
5. Example using {language} ({library})
6. Expected response

Make it copy-paste ready and well-documented.

prompts.generate_docs:
Generate API documentation for this endpoint:

Endpoint: {method} {path}
Description: {description}
Parameters: {parameters}
Request body: {request_schema}
Response: {response_schema}
Examples: {examples}

Create documentation with:
1. Endpoint overview
2. Authentication requirements
3. Request parameters table
4. Request body schema
5. Response codes and meanings
6. Response schema
7. Code examples (curl, JavaScript, Python)
8. Common errors and solutions

Format: {format} (Markdown/OpenAPI/Postman)
